{"title":"COVID-19 dialog for writeguard.com","description":"COVID-19 dialog for writeguard.com","tags":["gistpad"],"html":"<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/jquery-ui.js\"></script>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/themes/base/jquery-ui.css\"\n  media=\"screen\" />\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"style.css\" media=\"screen\">\n<script src=\"https://kit.fontawesome.com/1c27eae74d.js\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/3.2.1/css/font-awesome.min.css\"\n  media=\"screen\" />\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\"\n  href=\"https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css\" />\n\n<div id=\"dialog\" title=\"COVID-19\">\n  <i class=\"fas fa-biohazard\"></i>\n  <p>Due to the COVID-19 changing daily we have a new policy in effect on all shipments. Writeguard must have an ok on\n    each individual order saying that the customer we are shipping to will be availbale to receive shipments. If the\n    customer is available for shipments on specific days, please let us know the delivery date needed and we will ship\n    accordingly. </p>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"dialog2\" title=\"COVID-19\">\n  <p>Due to the COVID-19 changing daily we have a new policy in effect on all shipments. Writeguard must have an ok on\n    each individual order saying that the customer we are shipping to will be availbale to receive shipments. If the\n    customer is available for shipments on specific days, please let us know the delivery date needed and we will ship\n    accordingly.</p>\n</div>\n\n<button id=\"opener\">Open Dialog</button>\n\n<h4>Replacing / Extending jQuery UI with Font Awesome</h4>\n\n<div id=\"btn1\" />Volume</div>\n<div id=\"btn2\" />Volume</div>\n<div id=\"btn3\" />Volume</div>\